After the insurance approval my co payment was going to be only {$1000.00} and the rest would be covered by the insurance, unfortunately that was not the case, after the procedure was done I was charged {$3100.00}, I did not agree to these charges, I contacted my insurance and was told they paid the treatment which made me to believe the bill was settled. 
My complain is {$3100.00} was reported on my credit report by a collection agent I believe legally medical bills are not required to be reported on credit bureau I don't agree with these charges, the Insurance agree to pay for the procedure and my payment was only {$1000.00}

